Package: textmineR
Title: Functions for text mining and topic modeling
Version: 1.5
Date: 2015-07-26
Authors: "Thomas W. Jones <jones.thos.w@gmail.com>"
Maintainer: Thomas W. Jones <jones.thos.w@gmail.com>
Description: This package is an aid for text mining in R. Also, it implements 
    various functions related to topic modeling. It is designed to work with
		the "lda" package by J. Chang. 
Depends:
    R (>= 2.15),
    lda,
    parallel,
    Matrix,
    slam,
    RcppArmadillo,
    tm,
    RWeka
License: LGPL
LazyData: true
Suggests:
    wordcloud
LinkingTo: Rcpp,
    RcppArmadillo,
    RcppProgress
Imports:
    Rcpp,
    RcppArmadillo,
    RcppProgress
